overview: There's a new doctor in old Santa Fe, and it's Greer Garson. Director  Mervyn LeRoy's 1955 western also stars Dana Andrews, Cameron Mitchell, Lois Smith, Walter Hampden, Pedro Gonzales-Gonzales, Earl Holliman, Adele Jergens, Robert Wilke, Frank DeKova, Nick Adams, Douglas Kennedy, Ralph Moody and Louise Lorimer.
tagline: She was the one woman Rork didn't want in Santa Fe... but he'd kill anybody who'd try to make her leave...
title: Strange Lady in Town
